description:
Hello Elastics,

We're happy to announce that the 1st Elastic Meetup in Porto will be held on 22nd March in partnership with Syone, Elastic and Farfetch!

Venue: R. da Lionesa 446, Edifício G12, 4465-671, Leça do Balio

AGENDA
18:30 Warm Up and Networking
19:00 Welcome to Elastic Portugal!
19:15 Elastic New Features and Technical Enhancements (Matias Cascallares & Dale McDiarmid, Elastic)
20:00 Break
20:15 Farfetch experience with Elastic (Mário Barbosa & Vítor Saraiva, Farfetch)
20:50 Pizza, Beer, Networking and Chill

See you then!
location: F A R F E T C H
name: First Elastic Meetup in Porto
